{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-wrap-property-to-wrap-a-row-or-column","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-flexbox","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi svojstvo `flex-wrap` da pokrije red ili kolonu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>CSS flexbox ima funkciju za podelu fleksibilnog kontejnera u više redova (ili kolona). Po podrazumevanju, fleksibilni kontejner će sve fleksibilne elemente postaviti zajedno. Na primer, ceo red će biti na jednoj liniji.</p>\n<p>Međutim, korišćenje atributa <code>flex-wrap</code> sprečava da <code>CSS</code> pokrije delove. To znači da su dodatni delovi premešteni u novi red ili kolonu. Tačka za zaustavljanje gde se pokrivanje dešava zavisi od veličine delova i veličine kontejnera.</p>\n<p>CSS Takođe ima opcije za smer pokrivanja:</p>\n<ul><li><code>nowrap</code>: ovo su podrazumevani podešavanja, i ne uvija elemente.</li><li><code>wrap</code>: uvija elemente u više redova od vrha do dna ako je red, i od leve ka desno ako je kolona.</li><li><code>wrap-reverse</code>: uvija elemente u više redova od dna do vrha ako je red, i od desne ka levo ako je kolona.</li></ul>\n</section>","id":"587d78ad367417b2b2512afa","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Trenutna postavka ima previše kutija na jedan red. Dodajte atribut CSS <code>flex-wrap</code> na element <code>#box-container</code> i postavite mu vrednost <code>wrap</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pVaDAv/cQv9ZtG","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301114,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-wrap-property-to-wrap-a-row-or-column"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  #box-container {\r\n    background: gray;\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    height: 100%;\r\n\r\n  }\r\n  #box-1 {\r\n    background-color: dodgerblue;\r\n    width: 25%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-2 {\r\n    background-color: orangered;\r\n    width: 25%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n  #box-3 {\r\n    background-color: violet;\r\n    width: 25%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n  #box-4 {\r\n    background-color: yellow;\r\n    width: 25%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n  #box-5 {\r\n    background-color: green;\r\n    width: 25%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n  #box-6 {\r\n    background-color: black;\r\n    width: 25%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"box-container\">\r\n  <div id=\"box-1\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-2\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-3\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-4\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-5\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-6\"></div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Element za <code>#box-container</code> treba da ima svojstvo od <code>flex-wrap</code> ako ima vrednost <code>wrap</code>.</p>","testString":"const boxContainer = document.querySelector('#box-container');\r\nconst flexWrap = window.getComputedStyle(boxContainer)['flex-wrap'];\r\nassert.strictEqual(flexWrap, 'wrap');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-flexbox","dashedName":"use-the-flex-wrap-property-to-wrap-a-row-or-column","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-flexbox","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-shrink-property-to-shrink-items","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-align-items-property-in-the-tweet-embed","id":"587d78ad367417b2b2512afa","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  #box-container {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n  }\r\n  #box-1 {\r\n    background-color: dodgerblue;\r\n    align-self: center;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-2 {\r\n    background-color: orangered;\r\n    align-self: flex-end;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"box-container\">\r\n  <div id=\"box-1\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-2\"></div>\r\n</div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-wrap-property-to-wrap-a-row-or-column"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}